name: BRUCE pepe
additional_notices: Kindly be aware of liquidity-related risks. This notice is not directed at any project in particular, and is more of a cautionary reminder.

description.en:
What is the project about?
BRUCE pepe token is simply paying homage to a meme we all love and recognize.

What makes your project unique?
No pre-sales, no taxes, just stealth launch. BRUCE pepe burst onto the scene like a lightning-fast punch, burned liquidity pools with unmatched precision, and renounced its contract like a true master. 

History of your project.
BRUCE pepe was founded by an anonymous team in a stealth launch manner.

What’s next for your project?
BRUCE NFT launch in partnership with Bitmart, which will airdrop 8% of BRUCE supply to NFT holders.

What can your token be used for?
It's just a meme for culture!
